"na tveva tappaccayā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ "
"nirayaṃ upapajjeyya."
msgstr ""
"Because that might result in death or deadly pain. But when his body breaks "
